---
title: Roasted Barramundi and Mexican-Style Rice Bowls with Charred Corn Salad and Guacamole
description: These colourful bowls of Mexican-spiced roasted barramundi and rice are dolloped with ready-to-eat guac! A charred corn salad is added for a delicate smokiness.
